title: Furuya Minoru: Together with Me # 1-4
description:
Original title: Boku to Issho

Lewd, disgustinga and insanely hilarious manga by Furuya Minoru the creator of Ping Pong Club

A story about two kids who go to Tokyo after their mother died and their stepfather kicked them out of the house. In Tokyo they meet up with a fellow orphan named Shigeru Ito. Thus begins their cynical tale of laughter and depression.
